I started reading Game of Thrones to cope with the long wait before the next season. Not only are some characters pretty different from the show, there are some minor things that bother me much more than it should, such as Daenerys’ dark eyebrows and eye color.
Even though I wouldn’t want to see a thirteen year old Dany on the show, I decided to draw her more accurate to the book. I’ve also been trying to draw Rhaegar but he never comes out gorgeous enough *sigh*

Her dress is based on this img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-stat…
